'''Christian Read''' is an Australian comic book writer, best known for his work on ''Dunwich'', a take on the [[Wikipedia:Cthulhu|Cthulhu]] mythos, and ''The Watch''. His most recent work includes weird western ''The Eldritch Kid: Whisky and Hate'', ongoing supervillain series ''Unmasked'', and urban fantasy novel ''Black City''.

Read has written three stories for [[Dark Horse Comics|Dark Horse's]] ''[[Star Wars Tales]]'' series: "[[Nameless (comic story)|Nameless]]," "[[Apocalypse Endor]]," and "[[The Duty]]."

